<script>
            $(function(){
                $('#bar-app').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).show();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-app').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').hide();
                });
                $('#bar-up').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-up').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                });
            });
            </script>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(window).scroll(function() {
        var scrolls = $(this).scrollTop();
        if(scrolls > 100 && scrolls < 3800){
            $(".float-bar").show();
        }else{
            $(".float-bar").hide();
        }
    });

</script>

<script>

	$(function(){
		$(".seoTabContent ul .openOther").click(function(){
  			$(this).css("display","none");
  			$(this).closest("ul").find(".otherContent").css("display","block");
		})
  		$(".seoTab a").click(function(){
  			var $this=$(this);
	    	var i=$this.index();
	    	if($this.attr('class').indexOf("currentLink")>-1){
	    		return ;
	    	}else{
	    		$this.addClass("currentLink").siblings().removeClass("currentLink");
	    		$("#seoTabContent"+i).show().siblings().hide();
	    	}
  		})
	})
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
var currentUrl = '/nantong/s_tp9m5t12?guarantee_type=2';
//定义搜索参数
 var SEARCH_QUERY = 'standard_type=1';

function toFixNum(number,fractionDigits){   
	    with(Math){     
			return round(number*pow(10,fractionDigits))/pow(10,fractionDigits); 
		}
}
$quick_researchBtn = $('#quick_research');
/*
if($quick_researchBtn[0] && $quick_researchBtn[0].tagName && $quick_researchBtn[0].tagName.toUpperCase()=='A')
	$quick_researchBtn = $quick_researchBtn.parent();
*/
$quick_researchBtn.click(function(evt){    
    evt.preventDefault();
    var form = $('form.quick_research_form')[0];
    form.action = qsearch_url;
    form.method="get";
	if(Validator.validForm(form, true)){
		
		if($('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs')[0]){
			var cd_box_inp = $('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs'),
				val = cd_box_inp.val(),
				price = $('#loan_limit').val();
			cd_box_inp.val(price -  toFixNum(price*val/10,1));
		}
        form.submit();
    }

});

var form = $('form.quick_research_form')[0];
$(form).on('keydown',function(e){
    form.action = qsearch_url;
    form.method="get";
    if(e.keyCode==13){
        if(Validator.validForm(form, true)){
    	if($('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs')[0]){
    		var cd_box_inp = $('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs'),
    			val = cd_box_inp.val(),
    			price = $('#loan_limit').val();
    		cd_box_inp.val(price -  toFixNum(price*val/10,1));
    	}
            form.submit();
        }
    }	 
});
$(function(){
	Validator.config.hint_left_offset = 20;
    
	$('form').each(function(idx, form){
        Validator.initForm(form, true);
    });
    
	$('body').on('click','#save_info_btn',function(){
	    $form = $('#save_user_info_form');
            if(Validator.validForm($form)){
	        var querys = $form.serialize();
                var url = $form.attr('action') +'?'+querys; 
                PopLayer.iframe("about:blank");
                $form.submit(); 
	    }else{
                return false;
            }
	});    
	if($('#save_user_info_form').length)	
        _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', '/search/noresult.html']);

    $('.select_ul a').click(function(event){
        window.location.href = $(this).attr('href');
    });
    $('#fafangxingshi').sSelect({
        minWidth:155 
    }).change(function(){
        changeSel();
    });
    //页面间传递收入形式,对url重写
    $('#moreCondition a,.selected-list a,.ui-tab-nav-inner a').click(function(){
        var value = $('#fafangxingshi').val();
        if(parseInt(value)){
            var url = $(this).attr('href');
            var pattern = new RegExp('incometype=\\d','gi');
            if(pattern.test(url)){
                url = url.replace(pattern,'incometype='+value);
            }else{
                if(url.search(/\?/) !== -1){
                    url += '&incometype='+value;
                }else{
                    url += '?incometype='+value;
                }
            }
            $(this).attr('href',url);
        }
    })
    
    function changeSel(){
        if($('#fafangxingshi').length <= 0){
            return;
        }
        var value = $('#fafangxingshi').val();
        $('#box_user_income_by_card').hide();    
        $('#box_cash_receipts').hide();    
        if(value == '2'){
            $('#box_user_income_by_card').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,2);
            });    
        }
        if(value == '1'){
            $('#box_cash_receipts').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,1);     
            });    
        }
        if(value == '3'){
            $('#box_user_income_by_card').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,3);    
            });    
            $('#box_cash_receipts').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,3);    
            });    
        }
    }
    function modifyUrl(dom,num){
        var url = $(dom).attr('href');
        if(num == 1){
            if(url.indexOf('guwen') != -1){
                url += '&user_income_by_card=0';
            }else{
                url = url.replace(/f4x(\d*)(.*)/,"f4x0$2");   //消费不限等频道 
            }
        }else if(num == 2){
            if(url.indexOf('guwen') != -1){
                url += '&cash_receipts=0';
            }else{
                url = url.replace(/f4(x\d*)(x\d*)?(.*)/,"f4$1x0$3");
            }
        }
        var pattern = new RegExp('incometype=\\d','gi');
        if(pattern.test(url)){
            url = url.replace(pattern,'incometype='+num);
        }else{
			if(url.indexOf('?') != -1){
            	url += '&incometype='+num;
			}else{
            	url += '?incometype='+num;
			}
        }
        $(dom).attr('href',url);
    }
    changeSel();
});
</script>

            dnsimagesrc2 = "//static.rong360.com/upload/54f77443ec471bb357d19a6bf4fd2dd2.png?t="+t,
            statusimgsrc2 = "//perf.rong360.com/cdntest/result?source="+ encodeURIComponent(dnsimagesrc2) +"&status=",

            statusimgsrc3 = "//perf.rong360.com/cdntest/result?source="+ encodeURIComponent(dnsimagesrc3) +"&status=";

            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc+'ok&t=' + t;

            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc+'fail&t=' + t;

            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc2+'ok&t=' + t;

            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc2+'fail&t=' + t;

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(document).delegate("#footer", "mouseenter", function(){
		var panel = $(this).find(".panel");
		$(this).find("[data-flag]").click(function(){
			var flag = $(this).data("flag");
			panel.hide();
			$(panel[flag]).show();
		});
	});

		var panel = $("#footer").find(".panel");

<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        //var img = document.createElement('img');
        //img.src = get_ra() + '&pl=' + get_pl();
        $(document).append('<img src="' + get_ra() + '&pl=' + get_pl() + '&rl=' + get_rl() + '&ol=' + get_ol() + '&al=' + get_al() + '&rn=' + $('[ra-result-num]').html() + '" />');
    });
    function ajax_ra(url)
    {
        var img = document.createElement('img');
        img.src = get_ra() + '&aurl=' + encodeURIComponent(url) + '&pl=' + get_pl() + '&ol=' + get_ol() + '&al=' + get_al() + '&rn=' + $('[ra-result-num]').html();
    }
    function get_pl()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('.result [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_rl()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('.result [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        $('.rec [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_ol()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('[ra-data-ol]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-ol'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_al()
    {
        var al =[];
        $('[ra-data-al]').each(function(){
            al.push($(this).attr('ra-data-al'));
        });
        return al.join(',');
    }
    </script>
<script src="/static/js/ra.js"></script>
<script>
(function($){
    $.cookie = function(name, value, options){
        if (typeof value != 'undefined') { // name and value given, set cookie
            options = options || {};
            if (value === null) {
                value = '';
                options.expires = -1;
            }
            var expires = '';
            if (options.expires && (typeof options.expires == 'number' || options.expires.toUTCString)) {
                var date;
                if (typeof options.expires == 'number') {
                    date = new Date();
                    date.setTime(date.getTime() + (options.expires * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                } else {
                    date = options.expires;
                }
                expires = '; expires=' + date.toUTCString(); // use expires attribute, max-age is not supported by IE
            }
            var path = options.path ? '; path=' + options.path : '; path=/';
            var domain = options.domain ? '; domain=' + options.domain : '';
            var secure = options.secure ? '; secure' : '';
            document.cookie = [name, '=', encodeURIComponent(value), expires, path, domain, secure].join('');
        } else { // only name given, get cookie
            var reg = new RegExp("(?:^| )" + name + "=([^;]*)(;|$)"),
                result = reg.exec(document.cookie);
            return decodeURIComponent( (result && result[1]) || '');
        }
    }
})(jQuery);
function get_ra()
{
    var ra_pid = "eebfe4bccf330ca2c2a65bb928a5a166";
    if ($('#ra_pid').length > 0)
    {
        ra_pid = $('#ra_pid').val();
    }
    var url = "%2Fnantong%2Fs_tp9m5t12%3Fguarantee_type%3D2";
    var rf = encodeURIComponent(document.referrer);
    var host = "https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rong360.com";
    var abclass = $.cookie('abclass').split('_');
    if(abclass.length > 1)
    {
        abclass = abclass[1];
    }
    else
    {
        abclass = abclass[0];
    }
    var ext_str = '';
    
    var page_name = '';
                                      
            page_name += '&application_type=buxian';
            page_name += '&page_name=search';
                return '//g.rong360.com/u.gif?rid=' + ra_gc('RONGID') + '&access_id=' + '0jdth0br8abkc71qcvn1to1di0' + '&ca=search/index&tpl=/search_main/release/page/index.tpl&url=' + url + '&rf=' + rf + '&host=' + host + '&city=nantong&pid=' + ra_pid + '&uf=s_45c347fdea65c43a3fc9966dd720eff3&abclass=' + abclass + '&ga_csr=&ga_ccn=&ga_cmd=&ga_ctr=&rtm=' + ra_gc('__rtm') + '&ext=' +  encodeURIComponent(ext_str) + '&page_name=' + encodeURIComponent(page_name);
};
$(function(){
    $.json2param = function(json){
        var result = "";
        for(var item in json){
            if(json[item] != "" || json[item].toString() == "0"){
                result += item + "=" + json[item] + "&";
            }
        }
        return result.substring(0, result.length-1);
    };
    $.log=function(vo){
        var application_type = "9" || 9;
                        var ext = vo.ext?encodeURIComponent(vo.ext):"";
        var pageName = vo.page_name || "";
        var fr = vo.fr || "";
        var rfPageName = vo.rf_page_name || "";
        if(!(vo.page_name == "homepage" || vo.page_name == "about" || vo.page_name == "chedai_index" || vo.page_name == "choosecity")){
            var page_name = "page_name=" + pageName + "&application_type=buxian";
        }else{
            var page_name = "page_name=" + pageName;
        }       
        if(!(vo.page_name == "homepage" || vo.rf_page_name == "homepage" || vo.rf_page_name == "about" || vo.rf_page_name == "chedai_index" || vo.rf_page_name == "choosecity")){
            var rf_page_name = "page_name=" + rfPageName + "&application_type=buxian";
        }else{
            var rf_page_name = "page_name=" + rfPageName;
        }
                var params = {
            "rid": "" || "" || ra_gc('RONGID'),
            "rf": "",
            "host": encodeURIComponent("//www.rong360.com"),
            "city": $.cookie('cityDomain'),
            "abclass": "81",
            "ga_csr": "",
            "ga_ccn": "",
            "ga_cmd": "",
            "ga_ctr": "",
            "rtm": "", //add by caoxiaolin at 2013.12.10 for sem rtm
            "page_name": encodeURIComponent(page_name),
            "fr": fr,
            "rf_page_name": encodeURIComponent(rf_page_name),
            "platform": "pc",
            "channel": "daikuan",
            "application_type": "buxian",
            "ext": ext,
            "url": "%2Fnantong%2Fs_tp9m5t12%3Fguarantee_type%3D2",
            "real_id": vo.real_id?vo.real_id:""
        };
        var img = document.createElement('img');
        img.src = "//g.rong360.com/u.gif?" + $.json2param(params);
    };
    //点击统计
    $(document).delegate('[data-dpf-log]',"click", function(){
        var url = $(this).attr('href'),
            data = $(this).data("dpf-log");
        $.log({
            page_name: data.page_name
        });
    });
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function(){
		var tags = $("[data-log-event]"),
			vo = {
				//rongid
				"rid": "1fae01e6412b5b8110f0d508671baec7",
				//sessionid
				"access_id": "",
				//当前页面的pagename
				"page_name": "page_name=search",

				//事件id
				"event_name": "",
				//所带的参数
				"params": "",
				//来源
				"rf": document.referer || "",
				//日志接受时间
				"time_stamp": (new Date()).getTime(),
				//扩展参数
				"events_ext": ""
			};
		$(document).delegate("[data-log-event]","click",function(){
			var eventName = $(this).data("log-event"),
				params = $(this).data("params");
			vo.event_name = eventName;
			vo.params = params;
			var e = new Image();
			e.src = "//g.rong360.com/e.gif?" + $.json2param(vo);
		});
	});
</script>

<script>
            $(function(){
                $('#bar-app').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).show();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-app').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').hide();
                });
                $('#bar-up').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-up').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                });
            });
            </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    $(window).scroll(function() {
        var scrolls = $(this).scrollTop();
        if(scrolls > 100 && scrolls < 3800){
            $(".float-bar").show();
        }else{
            $(".float-bar").hide();
        }
    });

</script>

<div class="tip">选贷款太复杂？贷款助手小融来帮忙！</div>

<script>
            $(function(){
                $('#bar-app').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).show();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-app').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-app1');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                    $('.float-bar-ewm').hide();
                });
                $('#bar-up').mouseenter(function(){
                    $(this).addClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).removeClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).show();
                }); 
                $('#bar-up').mouseleave(function(){
                    $(this).removeClass('blue');         
                    $('div',this).addClass('bg-up');
                    $('span',this).hide();
                });
            });
            </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    $(window).scroll(function() {
        var scrolls = $(this).scrollTop();
        if(scrolls > 100 && scrolls < 3800){
            $(".float-bar").show();
        }else{
            $(".float-bar").hide();
        }
    });

</script>

<script>

	$(function(){
		$(".seoTabContent ul .openOther").click(function(){
  			$(this).css("display","none");
  			$(this).closest("ul").find(".otherContent").css("display","block");
		})
  		$(".seoTab a").click(function(){
  			var $this=$(this);
	    	var i=$this.index();
	    	if($this.attr('class').indexOf("currentLink")>-1){
	    		return ;
	    	}else{
	    		$this.addClass("currentLink").siblings().removeClass("currentLink");
	    		$("#seoTabContent"+i).show().siblings().hide();
	    	}
  		})
	})
</script>

<script src="https://www.rong360.com/static//scripts/jquery.select-1.3.6.js?v=201601181537" type="text/javascript"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
var currentUrl = '/nantong/s_tp9m5t12?guarantee_type=2';
//定义搜索参数
 var SEARCH_QUERY = 'standard_type=1';

function toFixNum(number,fractionDigits){   
	    with(Math){     
			return round(number*pow(10,fractionDigits))/pow(10,fractionDigits); 
		}
}
$quick_researchBtn = $('#quick_research');
/*
if($quick_researchBtn[0] && $quick_researchBtn[0].tagName && $quick_researchBtn[0].tagName.toUpperCase()=='A')
	$quick_researchBtn = $quick_researchBtn.parent();
*/
$quick_researchBtn.click(function(evt){    
    evt.preventDefault();
    var form = $('form.quick_research_form')[0];
    form.action = qsearch_url;
    form.method="get";
	if(Validator.validForm(form, true)){
		
		if($('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs')[0]){
			var cd_box_inp = $('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs'),
				val = cd_box_inp.val(),
				price = $('#loan_limit').val();
			cd_box_inp.val(price -  toFixNum(price*val/10,1));
		}
        form.submit();
    }

});

var form = $('form.quick_research_form')[0];
$(form).on('keydown',function(e){
    form.action = qsearch_url;
    form.method="get";
    if(e.keyCode==13){
        if(Validator.validForm(form, true)){
    	if($('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs')[0]){
    		var cd_box_inp = $('#_combox_inp_car_dkcs'),
    			val = cd_box_inp.val(),
    			price = $('#loan_limit').val();
    		cd_box_inp.val(price -  toFixNum(price*val/10,1));
    	}
            form.submit();
        }
    }	 
});
$(function(){
	Validator.config.hint_left_offset = 20;
    
	$('form').each(function(idx, form){
        Validator.initForm(form, true);
    });
    
	$('body').on('click','#save_info_btn',function(){
	    $form = $('#save_user_info_form');
            if(Validator.validForm($form)){
	        var querys = $form.serialize();
                var url = $form.attr('action') +'?'+querys; 
                PopLayer.iframe("about:blank");
                $form.submit(); 
	    }else{
                return false;
            }
	});    
	if($('#save_user_info_form').length)	
        _gaq.push(['_trackPageview', '/search/noresult.html']);

    $('.select_ul a').click(function(event){
        window.location.href = $(this).attr('href');
    });
    $('#fafangxingshi').sSelect({
        minWidth:155 
    }).change(function(){
        changeSel();
    });
    //页面间传递收入形式,对url重写
    $('#moreCondition a,.selected-list a,.ui-tab-nav-inner a').click(function(){
        var value = $('#fafangxingshi').val();
        if(parseInt(value)){
            var url = $(this).attr('href');
            var pattern = new RegExp('incometype=\\d','gi');
            if(pattern.test(url)){
                url = url.replace(pattern,'incometype='+value);
            }else{
                if(url.search(/\?/) !== -1){
                    url += '&incometype='+value;
                }else{
                    url += '?incometype='+value;
                }
            }
            $(this).attr('href',url);
        }
    })
    
    function changeSel(){
        if($('#fafangxingshi').length <= 0){
            return;
        }
        var value = $('#fafangxingshi').val();
        $('#box_user_income_by_card').hide();    
        $('#box_cash_receipts').hide();    
        if(value == '2'){
            $('#box_user_income_by_card').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,2);
            });    
        }
        if(value == '1'){
            $('#box_cash_receipts').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,1);     
            });    
        }
        if(value == '3'){
            $('#box_user_income_by_card').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,3);    
            });    
            $('#box_cash_receipts').show().find('a').each(function(){
                modifyUrl(this,3);    
            });    
        }
    }
    function modifyUrl(dom,num){
        var url = $(dom).attr('href');
        if(num == 1){
            if(url.indexOf('guwen') != -1){
                url += '&user_income_by_card=0';
            }else{
                url = url.replace(/f4x(\d*)(.*)/,"f4x0$2");   //消费不限等频道 
            }
        }else if(num == 2){
            if(url.indexOf('guwen') != -1){
                url += '&cash_receipts=0';
            }else{
                url = url.replace(/f4(x\d*)(x\d*)?(.*)/,"f4$1x0$3");
            }
        }
        var pattern = new RegExp('incometype=\\d','gi');
        if(pattern.test(url)){
            url = url.replace(pattern,'incometype='+num);
        }else{
			if(url.indexOf('?') != -1){
            	url += '&incometype='+num;
			}else{
            	url += '?incometype='+num;
			}
        }
        $(dom).attr('href',url);
    }
    changeSel();
});
</script>
#########################################################################################################################################################
<script type="text/javascript">
        var dnsimage = new Image(),
            dnsimage2 = new Image(),
            dnsimage3 = new Image(),
            dnsstatusimg = new Image(),
            _d = new Date(),
            t = _d.getTime(),
            dnsimagesrc = "//static.rong360.com/upload/54f77443ec471bb357d19a6bf4fd2dd2.png?t="+t,            
            statusimgsrc = "//perf.rong360.com/cdntest/result?source="+ encodeURIComponent(dnsimagesrc) +"&status=",

            dnsimagesrc2 = "//static.rong360.com/upload/54f77443ec471bb357d19a6bf4fd2dd2.png?t="+t,
            statusimgsrc2 = "//perf.rong360.com/cdntest/result?source="+ encodeURIComponent(dnsimagesrc2) +"&status=",

            dnsimagesrc3 = "//static.rong360.com/upload/54f77443ec471bb357d19a6bf4fd2dd2.png?t="+t,
            statusimgsrc3 = "//perf.rong360.com/cdntest/result?source="+ encodeURIComponent(dnsimagesrc3) +"&status=";

        dnsimage.onload = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc+'ok&t=' + t;
        }
        dnsimage.onerror = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc+'fail&t=' + t;  
        }

        dnsimage2.onload = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc2+'ok&t=' + t;
        }
        dnsimage2.onerror = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc2+'fail&t=' + t;  
        }

        dnsimage3.onload = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc3+'ok&t=' + t;
        }
        dnsimage3.onerror = function(){
            dnsstatusimg.src = statusimgsrc3+'fail&t=' + t;  
        }

        dnsimage.src = dnsimagesrc;
        dnsimage2.src = dnsimagesrc2;
        dnsimage3.src = dnsimagesrc3;        
    </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(document).delegate("#footer", "mouseenter", function(){
		var panel = $(this).find(".panel");
		$(this).find("[data-flag]").click(function(){
			var flag = $(this).data("flag");
			panel.hide();
			$(panel[flag]).show();
		});
	});
	$(document).delegate("#footer .panel", "mouseleave", function(){
		var panel = $("#footer").find(".panel");
		panel.hide();
	});
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        //var img = document.createElement('img');
        //img.src = get_ra() + '&pl=' + get_pl();
        $(document).append('<img src="' + get_ra() + '&pl=' + get_pl() + '&rl=' + get_rl() + '&ol=' + get_ol() + '&al=' + get_al() + '&rn=' + $('[ra-result-num]').html() + '" />');
    });
    function ajax_ra(url)
    {
        var img = document.createElement('img');
        img.src = get_ra() + '&aurl=' + encodeURIComponent(url) + '&pl=' + get_pl() + '&ol=' + get_ol() + '&al=' + get_al() + '&rn=' + $('[ra-result-num]').html();
    }
    function get_pl()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('.result [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_rl()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('.result [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        $('.rec [ra-data-pl]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-pl'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_ol()
    {
        var pl = [];
        $('[ra-data-ol]').each(function(){
            pl.push($(this).attr('ra-data-ol'));
        });
        return pl.join(',');
    }
    function get_al()
    {
        var al =[];
        $('[ra-data-al]').each(function(){
            al.push($(this).attr('ra-data-al'));
        });
        return al.join(',');
    }
    </script>

<script>
(function($){
    $.cookie = function(name, value, options){
        if (typeof value != 'undefined') { // name and value given, set cookie
            options = options || {};
            if (value === null) {
                value = '';
                options.expires = -1;
            }
            var expires = '';
            if (options.expires && (typeof options.expires == 'number' || options.expires.toUTCString)) {
                var date;
                if (typeof options.expires == 'number') {
                    date = new Date();
                    date.setTime(date.getTime() + (options.expires * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                } else {
                    date = options.expires;
                }
                expires = '; expires=' + date.toUTCString(); // use expires attribute, max-age is not supported by IE
            }
            var path = options.path ? '; path=' + options.path : '; path=/';
            var domain = options.domain ? '; domain=' + options.domain : '';
            var secure = options.secure ? '; secure' : '';
            document.cookie = [name, '=', encodeURIComponent(value), expires, path, domain, secure].join('');
        } else { // only name given, get cookie
            var reg = new RegExp("(?:^| )" + name + "=([^;]*)(;|$)"),
                result = reg.exec(document.cookie);
            return decodeURIComponent( (result && result[1]) || '');
        }
    }
})(jQuery);
function get_ra()
{
    var ra_pid = "eebfe4bccf330ca2c2a65bb928a5a166";
    if ($('#ra_pid').length > 0)
    {
        ra_pid = $('#ra_pid').val();
    }
    var url = "%2Fnantong%2Fs_tp9m5t12%3Fguarantee_type%3D2";
    var rf = encodeURIComponent(document.referrer);
    var host = "https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rong360.com";
    var abclass = $.cookie('abclass').split('_');
    if(abclass.length > 1)
    {
        abclass = abclass[1];
    }
    else
    {
        abclass = abclass[0];
    }
    var ext_str = '';
    
    var page_name = '';
                                      
            page_name += '&application_type=buxian';
            page_name += '&page_name=search';
                return '//g.rong360.com/u.gif?rid=' + ra_gc('RONGID') + '&access_id=' + '0jdth0br8abkc71qcvn1to1di0' + '&ca=search/index&tpl=/search_main/release/page/index.tpl&url=' + url + '&rf=' + rf + '&host=' + host + '&city=nantong&pid=' + ra_pid + '&uf=s_45c347fdea65c43a3fc9966dd720eff3&abclass=' + abclass + '&ga_csr=&ga_ccn=&ga_cmd=&ga_ctr=&rtm=' + ra_gc('__rtm') + '&ext=' +  encodeURIComponent(ext_str) + '&page_name=' + encodeURIComponent(page_name);
};
$(function(){
    $.json2param = function(json){
        var result = "";
        for(var item in json){
            if(json[item] != "" || json[item].toString() == "0"){
                result += item + "=" + json[item] + "&";
            }
        }
        return result.substring(0, result.length-1);
    };
    $.log=function(vo){
        var application_type = "9" || 9;
                        var ext = vo.ext?encodeURIComponent(vo.ext):"";
        var pageName = vo.page_name || "";
        var fr = vo.fr || "";
        var rfPageName = vo.rf_page_name || "";
        if(!(vo.page_name == "homepage" || vo.page_name == "about" || vo.page_name == "chedai_index" || vo.page_name == "choosecity")){
            var page_name = "page_name=" + pageName + "&application_type=buxian";
        }else{
            var page_name = "page_name=" + pageName;
        }       
        if(!(vo.page_name == "homepage" || vo.rf_page_name == "homepage" || vo.rf_page_name == "about" || vo.rf_page_name == "chedai_index" || vo.rf_page_name == "choosecity")){
            var rf_page_name = "page_name=" + rfPageName + "&application_type=buxian";
        }else{
            var rf_page_name = "page_name=" + rfPageName;
        }
                var params = {
            "rid": "" || "" || ra_gc('RONGID'),
            "rf": "",
            "host": encodeURIComponent("//www.rong360.com"),
            "city": $.cookie('cityDomain'),
            "abclass": "81",
            "ga_csr": "",
            "ga_ccn": "",
            "ga_cmd": "",
            "ga_ctr": "",
            "rtm": "", //add by caoxiaolin at 2013.12.10 for sem rtm
            "page_name": encodeURIComponent(page_name),
            "fr": fr,
            "rf_page_name": encodeURIComponent(rf_page_name),
            "platform": "pc",
            "channel": "daikuan",
            "application_type": "buxian",
            "ext": ext,
            "url": "%2Fnantong%2Fs_tp9m5t12%3Fguarantee_type%3D2",
            "real_id": vo.real_id?vo.real_id:""
        };
        var img = document.createElement('img');
        img.src = "//g.rong360.com/u.gif?" + $.json2param(params);
    };
    //点击统计
    $(document).delegate('[data-dpf-log]',"click", function(){
        var url = $(this).attr('href'),
            data = $(this).data("dpf-log");
        $.log({
            page_name: data.page_name
        });
    });
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function(){
		var tags = $("[data-log-event]"),
			vo = {
				//rongid
				"rid": "1fae01e6412b5b8110f0d508671baec7",
				//sessionid
				"access_id": "",
				//当前页面的pagename
				"page_name": "page_name=search",
				//访问的城市
				"city": "nantong" || "q",
				//事件id
				"event_name": "",
				//所带的参数
				"params": "",
				//来源
				"rf": document.referer || "",
				//日志接受时间
				"time_stamp": (new Date()).getTime(),
				//扩展参数
				"events_ext": ""
			};
		$(document).delegate("[data-log-event]","click",function(){
			var eventName = $(this).data("log-event"),
				params = $(this).data("params");
			vo.event_name = eventName;
			vo.params = params;
			var e = new Image();
			e.src = "//g.rong360.com/e.gif?" + $.json2param(vo);
		});
	});
</script>
